@host = http://localhost:3000
@conversationId = REPLACE_WITH_ID

### Send message (creates conversation if not provided)
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}",
  "input": "Hello, how are you?"
}

### Open SSE stream for a conversation
GET {{host}}/chat/stream/{{conversationId}}
Accept: text/event-stream

### Get conversation history (paginated)
GET {{host}}/chat/{{conversationId}}?limit=10

### Get messages before a given ISO date (cursor)
# GET {{host}}/chat/{{conversationId}}?limit=10&before=2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z

### List conversations
GET {{host}}/conversations?limit=50

### SSE for conversation creations
GET {{host}}/conversations/stream
Accept: text/event-stream
